title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected class
description: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? The output is 'MySomeClass'.
OB: The output of the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method is 'MySomeClass'.

SR: To reproduce the issue, call the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method with a classSet that is not the expected class.
